Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band View Video The Beatles White Album View BLACKPINK 3rd Mini Album [Deadline] Gray Version NewsView More Out 2.20: Danny Brown - Stardust Danny Brown's last albums Quaranta and Scaring The Hoes bookended the end of the XXX era. Enter Stardust - Danny's first album since entering sobriety sees him rediscover his love of music, curating the next wave of star talent, who were heavily inspired by his music while exploring their own journey. The album features collaborations with Underscores, Quadeca, Femtanyl, Jane Remove, Frost Children, 8485, JOHNNASCUS, IssBrokie, Nnamdi, Ta Ukarinka and Zheani - a hand-picked lineup curated by Danny Brown, as diverse as they are in the cohesive in the universe of Stardust.PREORDER Danny Brown - Stardust - Out 2.20.26 - WARP RECORDS Read more Out 2.27: Paul McCartney & Wings - Man On The Run Soundtrack Man On The Run (Music from the Motion Picture Soundtrack) is taken from the Amazon MGM Studios feature documentary Paul McCartney Man on the Run directed by Academy Award winner Morgan Neville. This set contains deep cuts and fan favourites from McCartney's post-Beatles career, soundtracking the journey of Paul’s emergence from the dissolution of the world’s biggest band to proving to critics and fans that not all great acts are impossible to follow. This album compiles many of the key recordings from the motion picture for the first time.PREORDER Paul McCartney & Wings - Man On The Run Soundtrack - Out 2.27.26 - CAPITOL Read more OUT THIS WEEK 2.13.26 Beck - Everybody's Gotta Learn Sometime [Red]Charli xcx - Wuthering Heights [Galaxy Green/Black Vinyl]Jeff Buckley - Live At Sin-e [Box]Jill Scott - To Whom This May Concern [Indie Exclusive Brown Swirl]Troye Sivan - Blue Neighbourhood 'Ten Years On' - 10th Anniversary [Blush Pink & Aqua Blue] Read more Video Out 2.6: Joji - Piss In The Wind Joji returns with long-awaited 4th studio album Piss In The Wind via Palace Creek. The new LP cements his place as one of the most distinctive and genre-defying artists of his generation, balancing haunting melodies with gritty yet atmospheric production. The album captures the quiet contradictions that always defined his music, wrestling inner turmoil into something strangely beautiful. Features PIXELATED KISSES, Past Won’t Leave My Bed, and more.Joji - Piss In the Wind - PALACE CREEK ...and don't miss the video (click below) ! Read more Out 2.6: Joe Bonamassa - B.B. King's Blues Summit 100 This groundbreaking project celebrates the centennial birthday of B.B. King, honoring his monumental legacy with a one-of-a-kind Collaboration Album. The album will feature a double album worth of curated tracks of B.B. King's most iconic songs, recorded/tracked by Blues Rock Icon Joe Bonamassa and his all-star band, with production led by 2-time Grammy-nominated producers Joe Bonamassa and Josh Smith. Joe Bonamassa - B.B. King's Blues Summit 100 - KTBA RECORDS Read more Out 2.6: Lorien Testard - Clair Obscur: Expedition 33 O.S.T. Sandfall Interactive, Kepler Interactive and Laced Records are banding together to bring Lorien Testard's breakout soundtrack for Clair Obscur: Expedition 33 to vinyl and CD. This 6LP box set has been thoughtfully sequenced by Testard to honour the game's three-act structure. The tracklist is drawn from the soundtrack album and bonus tracks, with in-game mixes used in many instances. All tracks have been specially mastered for the vinyl format.Lorien Testard - Clair Obscur: Expedition 33 O.S.T. - LACED RECORDS Read more OUT THIS WEEK 2.6.26 [HOT SELLER] Joji - Piss In the Wind[HOT SELLER] Joe Bonamassa - B.B.
